{"tid":2196503,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"中國移動買手機又出事","createTime":"2020-09-10T03:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T02:29:03.000Z","uid":86224,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4d642fa39d190a4287235f3d3f773892b2d312","tid":2196503,"uid":86224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"【跟進中國移動售賣假iPhone事宜】<br />\n<br />\n日前接到街坊求助，指在中國移動購買了一部iPhone後，回家發現電池並非原廠製造，因此手機沒有充電功能；還在手機的設定中發現，電池早在2019年11月時已充滿電一次。<br />\n<br />\n周先生帶同單據與保養證明書到Apple總行維修<br />\n👇🏼<br />\nApple總行要求周先生先向中移動門市反映<br />\n👇🏼<br />\n‼️怎料中移動回覆周先生聲稱「不會負責」‼️<br />\n<br />\n買手機時，門市已清晰表明是一手貨兼廠機，但收貨時發現內裏零件懷疑被偷龍轉鳳。<br />\n<br />\n呀洋將會去信海關、消委會、中國移動，要求就商品說明條例，正視上述情況，及聯絡記者，在必要時出報導召集更多街坊，與有類近經歷的苦主，一同申訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SheepWongChunYeung/photos/a.103014284447428/326308012118053/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSheepWongChunYeung%2Fphotos%2Fa.103014284447428%2F326308012118053%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=129d3133\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SheepWongChunYeung/photos/a.103014284447428/326308012118053/</a><br />\n所以話 check機要check清楚係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d07068b7c8939b9bd43325c9d156fab5d2210ae","tid":2196503,"uid":38904,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"喺支那動買嘢就預咗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e817efbf00f9cda56f4c2acf9479ddb205288983","tid":2196503,"uid":155095,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T03:25:45.000Z","msg":"想投訴黨企，傻的嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543a07a54c471f8a543bb1dd9b78f8974b5ab4f1","tid":2196503,"uid":109923,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"投訴黨企？當國安法冇到？"},{"pid":"de6